    "Name": "BattleMaster",
    "Details": "This variant is produced by Clan Sea Fox on Twycross for their second line forces. Based on Clan technology its armament closely mirrors the 3M, with four forward firing Series 2b ER medium lasers, a Type VI Streak SRM-6, a Type DDS 'Kingston' ER PPC in the right arm, and twin Series V machine guns in the left arm. Eighteen double heat sinks keep heat under control, but the Targeting Computer makes it easy for Clan warriors to defeat foes.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Command Mech</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.19</color></b>",
